1. *Male* deca su počela da se igraju u parku. (The little children started to play in the park.)

2. Ona je nosila *malo* crveno cveće u kosi. (She was wearing a little bit of red flower in her hair.)

3. Oni su danas dobili *malu* zaradu. (They got a small salary today.)

4. Ona je pokazala *malu* zahvalnost. (She showed a little bit of gratitude.)

5. Oni su izgubili *malu* količinu novca. (They lost a small amount of money.)